WEBVTT

00:01.317 --> 00:04.018
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.019 --> 00:07.989
Hey, holy moly,
guacamole, Normie. Hey, what?

00:07.990 --> 00:09.857
Huh?

00:09.891 --> 00:11.559
See that guy down there?

00:11.560 --> 00:13.078
I think that might
be Spanky McFarland

00:13.079 --> 00:14.329
from the old Little Rascals.

00:14.330 --> 00:15.263
Get out.
Yeah, I think so.

00:15.264 --> 00:16.931
Really?
Hey, I'll go ask him.

00:16.965 --> 00:18.899
I'll go check it out.

00:20.969 --> 00:22.903
(humming
The Little Rascals theme)

00:26.275 --> 00:28.042
Hey, how are you doing, Sid?

00:28.076 --> 00:30.011
Hi.
Hey, uh, my name's Cliff Clavin.

00:30.063 --> 00:31.212
Hello, Cliff.

00:31.213 --> 00:33.314
You know, I-I know
you've probably heard this

00:33.315 --> 00:34.683
a thousand times before,

00:34.684 --> 00:36.818
but you do resemble
that, uh, child actor

00:36.819 --> 00:38.487
Spanky McFarland
from The Little Rascals.

00:38.488 --> 00:40.305
Well, that's
because... 'Cause I'm one of

00:40.306 --> 00:42.173
Little Rascals fan
there ever was.

00:42.174 --> 00:44.476
I mean I've got every episode
on tape, you know.

00:44.477 --> 00:47.727
Well, except "Free Eats" and,
uh, "Captain Spanky's Showboat."

00:47.728 --> 00:48.563
That's great.

00:48.564 --> 00:50.699
Yeah, Alfalfa,
Darla, Buckwheat.

00:50.700 --> 00:51.733
(chuckles)

00:51.734 --> 00:52.767
Hey, I got to confess,

00:52.768 --> 00:55.286
I had quite a big crush
on Darla.

00:55.421 --> 00:56.755
I'll tell you, you know,

00:56.756 --> 00:58.523
if you were Spanky,
boy, I could sit here

00:58.524 --> 01:00.057
and chew on your ear for hours,

01:00.058 --> 01:03.161
you know, about the, you know,
"Happy Birthday, Mr. Hood"

01:03.195 --> 01:05.630
and the "He-Man
Women Haters Club."

01:05.631 --> 01:07.649
And remember the sound the cake
made coming out of the oven?

01:07.650 --> 01:09.851
Was it...
(makes groaning noise)

01:09.885 --> 01:11.352
Huh?

01:11.386 --> 01:12.954
So, uh, are-are you Spanky?

01:12.988 --> 01:14.088
Nope.

01:14.122 --> 01:15.523
Ah.

01:15.524 --> 01:16.558
Take care.

01:16.559 --> 01:17.892
Catch you later.

01:17.977 --> 01:20.161
You are Spanky, aren't you?

01:20.196 --> 01:22.330
Oh, yeah.

01:23.666 --> 01:24.733
(theme song begins)

